OL,3,CLidl to give staff body cameras as
OL,4,Cshoplifting surges
OL,6,FLidl will roll out body cameras to
OL,7,Fstaff in its stores after a surge in
OL,8,Fshoplifting and violence towards
OL,9,Fworkers.
OL,11,FThe store claimed this would make it
OL,12,Fthe first UK supermarket firm to
OL,13,Fensure bodycams were used in every
OL,14,Fstore, although it is understood it
OL,15,Fwould not be required for every staff
OL,16,Fmember.
OL,18,FOther retailers, such as Tesco, have
OL,19,Fprovided workers with the option to
OL,20,Fwear the cameras or launched trials
OL,21,Fin recent months.
